<template>
  <button @click="fetchData">Clicca</button>
</template>

<script>
import axios from "axios";

export default {
  name: "AgendaPage",
  methods : {
    async fetchData(){
      try {
        const response = await axios.get('ServletGetBookingsForUser',{params : {action : 'web',stato : '1'}})
        console.log(response.data);
      }catch (e){
        console.error(e);
      }
    }
  }
}
</script>
